Creates a photo magazine from Instagram photos

This extension works on instagram.com. When you navigate there it will create a magazine from your Instagram feed.

You can choose to add more images or to watch your feed over time.

** This is not affiliated with Instagram. I made this myself. **

Feel free to send me an email with feedback. Jacques dot Applebaum @ gmail
